、`17` |\n| 产品行为 / UX / 验收 | `需求/` 对应编号 |\n| 代码落地模块地图 | 用户明示后写 `docs/AI/` |\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":40,"fileSize":2751,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":40},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-fa183fdb-da6e-468f-9525-bff3972c0d87-4\nfc_0fab84f5-b364-9561-9226-f67edfe83c40_3","startedAtMs":"1784782770608","completedAtMs":"1784782770748"},"model_call_id":"64ed3551-d7b9-4668-b2f9-5e28e05e4b02-1-4zcn","session_id":"5fe2590b-d41a-4c9d-bd28-d429f96b8f06","timestamp_ms":1784782770712}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-fa183fdb-da6e-468f-9525-bff3972c0d87-5\nfc_0fab84f5-b364-9561-9226-f67edfe83c40_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc","limit":80},"result":{"success":{"content":"---\ndescription: packages/rpg-engine 纯引擎边界\nglobs: packages/rpg-engine/**\nalwaysApply: false\n---\n\n# 引擎包边界（rpg-engine）\n\n详情：[05](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/05-技术选型与工程边界.md)、[19](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)、[02](../../docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md)。\n\n## 必须执行\n\n- **禁止** import：`react`、`react-dom`、`next`、`@xyflow/*`。\n- **禁止** `window` / `document` / `localStorage`（测试可注入）。\n- **EngineHost 单例**由 server/壳持有；本包提供 create/host API。\n- **CallSession** 在 Host 内存；`frozenCard`；同 user 通话互斥。\n- Composer 只读；EffectExecutor 仅出口/Free 管线；工具只登记 candidate。\n- **FreeCallPostPipeline** 为 Free 挂机唯一总入口（可注入）；v1 = 有效门闩 + MemoryCommit +（有 candidate 则 ExitSelector）；禁 transcript 隐式扫描。\n- Free Session.`packageId === \"__free__\"`；禁止 load 该哨兵为故事目录。\n- 媒介经 **EffectSink**；逻辑写 Profile 在 Executor。\n- 持久化：userId + Content/SaveGame JSON；日志旁路 jsonl 约定见 19。\n- 本包只被 Next **server**（`app/api` / `*.server.ts` / `utils/server`）/ 壳 / Vitest 引用；**禁止** Studio V2 Client（含 `bis` / `pageComponents` / `typeFiles` / `ajaxProxy`）任何 import（含 type）。\n- **存取：** 经 Port 注入（见技术设计 [23](../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)）；**禁止**本包内长期保留 `node:fs` / `better-sqlite3` 实现。本机实现落在 `apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/`。\n- 条件求值结构化谓词；禁 `eval`。\n- **对外门面：** `src/index.ts` **允许且鼓励**聚合导出；**合法调用方**只 `import from \"@airpc/rpg-engine\"`，禁依赖方深挖内部模块。\n- **测试**放 `packages/rpg-engine/tests/`，禁止与 `src/` 平放 `*.test.ts`。\n- **目录职责聚类：** 内部域文件增多时按异责 ≥4 分子目录（host/session/memory…）；不为空壳先建单文件空目录。\n\n## 默认执行\n\n- 公共导出收敛于包入口；Port 接口在本包；LLM/Realtime 实现不进本包。\n- Effect plan / ledger / 锁决策表遵循需求 16、19。\n- Vitest 覆盖 Resolver、Exit、Free pipeline、Profile 隔离、幂等。\n\n## 禁止事项\n\n- GPIO / ALSA / 旧 relay / expertReferral 上帝模块。\n- 把 React Flow layout 当运行真源。\n- 强迫 Studio 深引引擎内部路径「绕过门面」。\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":40,"fileSize":2554,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":40},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-fa183fdb-da6e-468f-9525-bff3972c0d87-5\nfc_0fab84f5-b364-9561-9226-f67edfe83c40_4","startedAtMs":"1784782770643","completedAtMs":"1784782770797"},"model_call_id":"64ed3551-d7b9-4668-b2f9-5e28e05e4b02-1-4zcn","session_id":"5fe2590b-d41a-4c9d-bd28-d429f96b8f06","timestamp_ms":1784782770764}
