gineIOModule/`。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. 为什么拆\\n\\n引擎是纯领域逻辑，将来可嵌入：\\n\\n| 宿主 | IO 形态（示例） |\\n|------|-----------------|\\n| Studio V2 / 本机 Next | `engineIOModule`：JSON+fs + SQLite + jsonl |\\n| 电话机壳 | 设备私有存储 / 只读 Content 包 |\\n| 纯浏览器 | **不本地 IO**；经 XHR→后端再落盘 |\\n\\n存储方案随平台变；**剧情与会话规则不变**。故：程序上 Port 化，物理上 IO 实现离开 `packages/rpg-engine`。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 2. 拓扑\\n\\n```text\\nBrowser（仅意图与展示）\\n  ↓ XHR\\nNext  [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":58,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-2eb21ce2-0299-413e-82d2-ac1348a1f696-6\\nfc_1219b489-8953-9bd2-97f2-34aa8c221d3d_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"ProfilePort|persistProfile|saveProfile|ensureProfile|loadProfile\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-2eb21ce2-0299-413e-82d2-ac1348a1f696-6\\nfc_1219b489-8953-9bd2-97f2-34aa8c221d3d_1\",\"offset\":0},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"pattern\":\"ProfilePort|persistProfile|saveProfile|ensureProfile|loadProfile\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine\",\"outputMode\":\"content\",\"workspaceResults\":{\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine\":{\"content\":{\"matches\":[{\"file\":\"packages/rpg-engine/tests/host/free-call-pipeline.test.ts\",\"matches\":[{\"lineNumber\":56,\"content\":\"    await host.ensureProfile(\\\"demo-user\\\");\",\"contentTruncated\":false,\"isContextLine\":false},{\"lineNumber\":105,\"content\":\"    await host.ensure [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":59,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\"Reviewing persistProfile.ts,\",\"session_id\":\"5df7473c-b605-4b3a-9f07-31e036300ac3\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784782376414}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":65,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"st